<br>
It took us about 3 hours total to get 9 wingblades on Saturday just once the lord and guardian were left. (we brought up reinforcements though - took about 30-45 mins) <br>
<br>
It took us about 5 hours to summon 30+ people to 4, finish off 4th island, summon another 12 to 5th, and get that stupid 5th island clearing done (had never done it before)<br>
<br>
This was all done with between 28-35 people levels 52-60 avg level about 56 or 57.<br>
<br>
We killed about 15 Spiroc Lords for the 9 blades.<br>
<br>
Count on that much time for each piece if you are getting summoned to 4th and clearing 5th for the first time.<br>
<br>
P.S. all the strategy guides say that you will get at least 2 or 3 vanquishers on first pull. Sounds terrible. We in fact got one and had to sit there with 5 birds mezzed and a tank on guardian for about 15 mins while we tried desparately to get another vanquisher to come. I finally made everyone camp and started the pull from another area. (this is after I died on pull and my corpse was warped to island one - gee thanks VI)<br>
<br>
So watch out for the strategy guides. They are not always 100% right. Don't start killing little birdies till you have at least 2 vanquishers dead.<br>
<br>
Hopefully that helps.<br>
